# Sync mukmin1 and mukmin-ngo

After making any file changes in this workspace, sync the local dev copy to the git repo copy:

```powershell
powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "C:\Code\mukmin1\scripts\sync-from-mukmin1.ps1"
```

- **Source:** `C:\Code\mukmin1` (local dev)
- **Target:** `C:\Code\mukmin-ngo` (git repo / server copy)
- **Direction:** always mukmin1 → mukmin-ngo (never reverse unless the user explicitly asks)

Run the sync at the end of tasks that modify project files. Do not skip because the user said "always sync."

Do not commit or push to `mukmin-ngo` unless the user explicitly asks.

If sync fails (exit code ≥ 8), report the error and retry or fix before finishing.
